data.description: Beautiful arches in Formal dining area and office and sunken living room.  Large kitchen and breakfast area, lots of cabinets, huge fridge and more.  Plenty of extra space for office and more. Home also features 2 tankless water heaters. In back is a 2,000sf brick paver patio surrounding a sparkling pool with a brick and wrought iron fence with additional land beyond. Whole house has gas generator. Seller is offering a $10000.00 buyer incentive towards closing costs, prepaids or interest rate buydown.  NO HOA! From the kitchen area exit the sliding glass doors to your private patio perfect for morning coffee or entertaining.  There is so much more to see, call for your appointment today.
